io.craigmiller160.school.entity

Class Student

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.craigmiller160.school.entity.Student
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Student>

    @Entity
public class Student
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Student>, java.io.Serializable
    An entity that defines a student taking courses. It contains the attributes that define the student, as well as a list of all courses the student is taking.

    THREAD SAFETY: This class is NOT thread-safe. Its state is not synchronized, and instances of it should be handled in a way that is not shared between threads.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    craig
